high_descs: Go to the coffee table and then go to the countertop to your right.
Pick up the knife on the countertop nearest to the wall.
Go back to the coffee table to your right.
Put the knife on the coffee table.
Turn right, walk straight and then go to the sink on the countertop to your right.
Pick up the knife on the countertop.
Turn right, walk straight and then go to the coffee table to your right.
Put the knife behind the knife already there on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the knives on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right and approach the kitchen counters ahead.
Of the two knives on the counter, pick up the one on the right.
Turn around to the small circular coffee table.
Place the knife down on the table.
Turn back to the counter you got the knife from.
Pick up the remaining knife on the counter.
Return to the small table you put the first knife down on.
Put the second knife down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place two knives on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the counter top.
Pick up knife from the counter top
Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the coffee table.
Place knife on the coffee table
Head straight, then proceed to turn right towards the counter top.
Pick up knife from the counter top
Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the coffee table.
Place knife on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Arrange knife on the coffee table
